# SevenAuto

- Monorepo code lives under `dashboard/`: Turborepo + pnpm. Apps: `apps/web` (Next), `apps/api` (Nest). Shared: `packages/ui`, `packages/libs`, `packages/eslint-config`, `packages/typescript-config`.
- From `dashboard/`, use `pnpm dev`, `pnpm build`, `pnpm lint`, `pnpm check-types`.
- Root `README.md` and `docs/getting-started.md` document onboarding; run pnpm from `dashboard/` only (`tools/` is a placeholder, not for running the app).
- When changing the API, read `src/modules/app.module.ts` and `src/modules/env/env.service.ts` for env contract and global wiring.
